Author: cryptoenterprise
Title: 💠 DIW 💠 [ANN] [ICO] 💠 DIWtoken.com 💠 Decentralize Security
Body: To my fellow community and crypto friends,  I'm sure we all feel somewhat anxious, exhausted and perhaps disappointed with a few certain events that have happened during the last few months - and im not talking about DIW Token alone, im also talking about the entire market in general! I wanted to express myself because I, along side others in this community, have waited long for things to happen - not saying actions have not been taken and executed, but certain things have delayed and postponed DIW Tokens roadmap and caused what we might call a ripple in the pond. So I will stop beating around the bush and get to my point...  Questions have arose ever since DIW Tokens ICO ended and we hit the exchanges, questions like, Why is the token price so low? Perhaps you are one of those early investors (just like me) who spent many ETH to participate in this ICO and now you cannot see any profit...So why has this happened?  There are many aspects as to what drove the price to this position, and created this uncertainty and I believe you should spare some time to read the reasons and my analysis below.  1. Facts are facts, Bitcoin and Ethereum are the leading coins in the market, so it's as clear as daylight to know that when the market is bearish and the main coins like BTC and ETH go down, then everything will tumble down with them and hit rock bottom. This is the same for ALL coins especially for ICOs that are trying to come up into the crypto space and become part of the "larger pond" - the market.  2. Another point that has come to mind is, when the market is in the "bloody" state that it is now, then people tend to worry, panic and be weary of how to invest or trade. For example, panic sellers not many but a few have made bid orders below a certain degree which basically means that with the small volume of Ethereum that currently exists, then the outcome would be the low price that we all see now. Truth be said, this is not a realistic price because there is a small volume in trading.  3. A sub-question that has popped up as i was analyzing all the likely reasons to our current condition is, the DIW team has not fully delivered and executed some important things, in effect causing uncertainty and doubt within the community. One important issue is the Token Distribution! Many members of the community including myself, continuously mentioned that we did not want the bounty tokens distributed prior to hitting the exchanges. So when we actually hit the exchanges, there were no buyers and the reason being is that the bounty had not been distributed yet. Waiting for the bounty to be distributed and waiting for things to settle down before making any buy orders would of been the wiser choice.  4. Burning of Tokens! We expected that the team would burn the tokens after bounty distribution, and i believe that the price has been effected due to this too. The circulating supply has not been put down in writing or announced anywhere so this has created uncertainty, confusion and we the community need to see these numbers.  5. Something that is on my mind but noticeable by other members of the community is the 2 exchanges that we have been listed to. Latoken and IDex are not popular when it comes to ICOs, they have some volumes but they don't have high volumes so this has effected the attitude of members too. The fact that the DIW team collected under 2000ETH throughout the ICO has made it difficult for them to enter into a better exchange with higher volume but I for one has seen ICOs join smaller exchanges in the beginning and then join much larger exchanges later. So i believe that this has also played some role in the whole price.  So these are the reasons i feel have affected the price of DIW Token, and i hope everyone see this and takes note to what i mentioned because it was spoken with all honesty.  Finally i believe that after what was mentioned above, we need to consider these things and I for one will continue to support the team as i've been doing so far.

Author: hexaman
Title: 💠 DIW 💠 [ANN] [ICO] 💠 DIWtoken.com 💠 Decentralize Security
Body: Original DIW tokens allocated for ICO were 700 million (70%) Original DIW tokens allocated for the team were 150 million (15%) If for example only 100 million tokens were sold after all during private, Pre & ICO, then the final number of tokens in circulation will be 1/7 of the original. Thus, in this case, team will get 1/7 of 150 million which calculates to 21.4 million DIW tokens. To summarise, the team will be left with 15% of the total DIW token supply whatever happens. It’s all the same.

Author: DIW
Title: 💠 DIW 💠 [ANN] [ICO] 💠 DIWtoken.com 💠 Decentralize Security
Body: Looking into your comments above, indeed the money raised is making things run slower and more difficult but its something reasonable and we do not have any reasons to hide behind this. On the other hand, we believe in our project and our team wants to make this work, even if it takes us longer than expected.  We are indeed doing many things and the postponement of the ICO has played a role as to why we are behind schedule. You can see our daily progress in regards to counting the tokens and trying to get all the robots, scammers and duplicates removed. People are trying various ways to scam us, even with duplicates, they make it hard for us to catch them.  Stay tuned as we will be delivering one thing at a time, even if it takes a bit longer to get everything delivered. We have been here from the beginning of the project and we will continue to be here to deliver the next phases of our product even if we have to pass through obstacles to accomplish this.  We have the support of thousands of contributors and we believe many of them will see us as we really are; a team of individuals who want to make a decentralized solution that will ensure everyone can safeguard sensitive information without the fear of ending up in the hands of organisations or third party individuals. This is what we started doing and this is what we will continue to do.

Body: From telegram  The reasons for the perceived delay are: 1. Multiple groups of people as well as multiple entities / organisations for listing a new cryptocurrency in exchanges are involved. Coordination, entry validation and approval takes time. 2. Seeing how the market’s state currently is, management is trying to limit the damage to everyone’s interest by coordinating the timing that we will hit the exchanges and distribute Bounty rewards. 3. As stated, Bounty and Airdrop participants will be the last ones to receive their tokens for obvious reasons – we wish to protect everyone whose supported our project during pre-sale and ICO the most. 4. Bounty rewards have been counted – we are waiting for favourable conditions to proceed with everything – stand by for further announcements next week. We wish to deeply thank everyone for your understanding, patience and support and wish to apologise for any inconvenience. Please keep in mind that we are working hard, having in mind everyone’s interests.

Author: DIW
Title: 💠 DIW 💠 [ANN] [ICO] 💠 DIWtoken.com 💠 Decentralize Security
Body: Hello - You are correct, once the hard cap is reached the ICO will stop and that could happen any time, even before the 31st of May.         - Regarding the progress bar, one will be added on our website soon.    Quote from: starb on May 05, 2018, 11:09:37 AM hello - can you please explain what will drive the price of this token up from an investment perspective? the whitepaper says it is utility token only to be used in system with no value.  Hello - Every ERC-20 token is aiming to be a utility token due to legalities. A token cannot be listed on exchanges if it's not a utility token because it would be subject to security laws in different countries and would cause legal issues.  The price of any token, not just DIW token, is mostly affected by demand and supply. We believe this project stands out for it’s practicality and it’s immediate application to daily online uses which is something missing from the market right now. The progress of the development made by the founders and the team and the adherence to the roadmap will increase the demand for our token and therefore make it a good choice for contributors.

Author: tendy263
Title: 💠 DIW 💠 [ANN] [ICO] 💠 DIWtoken.com 💠 Decentralize Security
Body: The transfer and storage of personal data is a rather personal and touchy subject in most people’s lives as the data in question often comprises of intimate and private information. What makes most individuals skeptical about bringing their personal data online is the high rate at which sensitive data is being intercepted or stolen globally resulting in grave consequences for the victims.  For professionals who conduct their businesses online is not easy to get strangers to trust you as most fear being scammed or being left with substandard products, services or even nothing. Companies have not been spared of the scourge of online security breaches and some have even fallen victim to online scams.  DIW’s unique concept plans to put an end to the problems that I have highlighted above. The plan is to introduce a global blockchain based network which will be completely equipped with its own ecosystem and currency, hence the name DIW. The acronym DIW stands for ’ Digital Identification Wallet’ but the project’s scope of applications goes far beyond just a cryptocurrency wallet.

The event was kicked off by our advisor Simon Cocking’s keynote speech “What makes for a successful ICO Campaign?”, where DIW was featured as one of the latest ICOs to watch. Moreover, the cherry on the cake was definitely the fact that we have the auspicious opportunity to meet these individuals again, as well as new like-minded individuals, at the Cryptocurrency World Expo in Berlin on the 21st and 22nd of March!

Author: DIW
Title: 💠 DIW 💠 [ANN] [ICO] 💠 DIWtoken.com 💠 Decentralize Security
Body: Hello cryptospacemedia  and thanks for your query.  Yes, that's the whole point of our project! Our vault will allow you to store your cryptocurrency. Once our global network and escrow services are up and running, you will be able to exchange services with other network members in a fully transparent environment as everyone will have to pass KYC / KYS screening. It will be next to impossible to get scammed. Furthermore, all network members will eventually feature their own rating score improving trust. To make sure that your transaction will go as smoothly as possible and especially if we are talking about larger amounts, an escrow service in the form of digital smart contracts will allow you to preset the conditions of the transaction. The payment amount will be placed on hold and the payment will only go through if these predetermined conditions have been met.  Thank you.

Author: DIW
Title: 💠 DIW 💠 [ANN] [ICO] 💠 DIWtoken.com 💠 Decentralize Security
Body: I have seen that you never received a reply.  Your question is fundamental to our product.  Our platform acts primarily as a wallet. A wallet or a vault that gives you access to your information, passwords and data. An access point to your virtual life. But you don't want a product that's used just for one thing. The largest organisations provide a variety of products. Similarly DIW will primarily give you the access point to save the information but also to become KYC approved an a society that is transparent, thats the Global Directory, also it will allow you to pay for products on other websites, so that Cryptocurrency get more adopted in daily life, it will allow you to have an escrow for specific products as today we find it difficult to trust individuals online (the directory will also help due to the KYC nature), and an expansion it will allow you to hold Electronic Health Records.  Our vision is to include a variety of modules/addons. Our vault is the fundamental piece of the puzzle!  Our idea was to make something that will profit DIW in the future, but will also solve a real problem. Without the end-solution in mind, which is helping secure our virtual life, but not by being restrictive but rather than providing alternative solutions to what we use today, makes a huge difference than just developing a product.

Author: lipochka_s
Title: 💠 DIW 💠 [ANN] [ICO] 💠 DIWtoken.com 💠 Decentralize Security
Body: How can you store personal information, especially passwords on the Internet? Security? Who can better store my information than I do? And if the scammers break the system, who can help me get the lost? Words forgive - it does not help! I can not trust anyone but me!

Author: DIW
Title: 💠 DIW 💠 [ANN] [ICO] 💠 DIWtoken.com 💠 Decentralize Security
Body: We totally understand what you are saying. You most likely are one of the millions of users who save passwords and data on a piece of paper, or on a drive stored locally.  Millions have now started to trust online software as password lockers and savers. What we are offering is something larger than just a password locker for people who already trust other organisations to save their data. Our system will have three aspects that our competitors cannot offer: 1) No single access from a single organisation. Meaning that a single person or organisation cannot access your data or have secret agreements with other organisations to share such information 2) Our second advantage is that our vault is built not just for passwords, but an access point to a different modules, like the Health Care, Global Directory, etc. 3) All of our members' valuable data will be stored on the blockchain so no one will actually have the data. Everyone will have just a tiny, unusable piece of them. They will only re-construct once you login via a highly secure access point. For further security while accessing the vault, a hardware wallet will be offered.

Title: 💠 DIW 💠 [ANN] [ICO] 💠 DIWtoken.com 💠 Decentralize Security

Author: DIW
Title: 💠 DIW 💠 [ANN] [ICO] 💠 DIWtoken.com 💠 Decentralize Security
Body: Check out our Press Release article on CCN.com!  DIWtoken.Com Crowdfunding: the Solution to Data Breach & Crypto Currency Spending       No Aspect of human life, including business and government affairs, can escape the effect of exchanging digital data. Data breaches pose a continuous direct threat to the stability and security of our global system.  Global Reaction  Everyday people are concerned. Multiple hacks have distributed millions of individuals’ sensitive personal data. Industry professionals are also becoming increasingly weary regarding the effect these data breaches may have on their businesses. Governments also face data breach issues. The FBI recently warned that ‘advanced persistent threat’ cyber attackers are increasingly targeting sensitive information.  A Valid Concern  Based on recent data, staggering 60 data records per second have been continually stolen since 2013!  This trend will get worse as time passes by unless fundamental changes take place.  Utilising Crypto Currency  In a period of just 12 months, the total market cap of all crypto currencies has seen an increase of 1700%.  However, there is a catch: Crypto currency is solely used within the crypto community and not in everyday life. It is evident that there is a major need for crypto currency to be widely accepted by the global retail sales leader – e-commerce.  The DIW Solution  DIW plans to bridge and solve both aforementioned issues with the introduction of its global, blockchain-based, decentralised network complete with its own ecosystem and currency.  To gain access into the network, members will be provided with a Secure Vault, where they will be able to store their entire ‘Digital Life’ including documents such as identities, passports, KYC & KYS, financial, contracts, health records as well as login details.  Organizations as well as individuals around the globe, will be able to join in and exchange their services in the form of a Global Directory. The network will ensure that their identity is validated and their details accurate. Transactions will be completed in full transparency and all network members will be able to see each member’s real life performance in the form of a rating score.  The DIW token will be used and accepted throughout the network for transactions between its members, enabling higher security. Additional security services such as a digital contract-based escrow service will also be offered.  To top it all up and follow the crypto currency trend, DIW plans to introduce its own Payment Gateway that will be easily integrated within e-commerce websites accepting both fiat as well as Crypto currencies enabling the utilisation of crypto currencies in everyday life.  DIW’s Crowdfunding  DIW plans to proceed with a crowdfunding that will enable the fruition of its project. Details in regards to pricing, whitepaper release as well as roadmap will be disclosed progressively within the upcoming weeks. To participate and stay informed, visit DIW’s website and join their Whitelist that is currently open.  To find out more and submit your entry to the whitelist visit https://diwtoken.com  Participate on the Whitelist and become an early backer of DIW https://diwtoken.com  Explainer Video – https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bNhMpqJAQHo  Find DIW on Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/diwtoken/ Follow DIW on Twitter – https://twitter.com/diwtoken Official DIW Telegram Group – https://t.me/diwtoken DIW on Bitcointalk – https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2567416
